All the funds go to support quality education for disadvantaged young people across the Middle East, Asia and Africa
Match for Hope has raised over $19.5 million, giving thousands of children hope for a brighter future

beIN SPORTS 5.title_en: Al Ittihad Club (KSA) vs Shabab Al Ahli (UAE) - AFC Champions League Elite 2025/2026 - West MD2
beIN SPORTS 5.desc_ar: This will be the first meeting between Al-Ittihad and Shabab Al Ahli in AFC Champions League Elite history; teams from Saudi Arabia have won seven of their last eight games in the competition against teams from UAE, however, the one loss in this run was Al-Ittihad’s 1-2 loss to Al Wahda in their opening matchday of the 2025-26 season. Al-Ittihad have lost each of their last three AFC Champions League Elite games, their joint-longest run of such games in the competition, including a 1-2 loss to Al Wahda on Matchday 1; Al-Ittihad have never lost each of their first two games of an AFC Champions League Elite campaign and only twice have they failed to win any of their first two games.
